snippet.title: Ultra C
snippet.description:
Lee and James are a couple of friends that like to play video games on the internet.  New videos every single day!

Here's how our upload schedule works:
     Monday, Tuesday, Thursday, Friday:  Short playthroughs (games that typically take 12-16 episodes, with a couple of hours of content total)
     Wednesday:  One-off videos!  Sometimes something new, sometimes an old favorite.
     Saturday + Sunday:  Anything we're passionate about at the moment.  For now, it's going to be Nova Drift!

The 'C' in 'Ultra C' can stand for several things:
     Competitive - Lee and James compete to see who sucks more!
     Co-op - Lee and James work together and try to suck less!
     Companionless - Either Lee or James is playing a game by themselves.
     Challenger - We compete with our friends to see who's the best!
     ...and very likely more types in the future!
